text: Evadne is a genus of onychopods in the family Podonidae. There are at least four described species in Evadne. ==Species== * Evadne anonyx Sars 1897 * Evadne nordmanni Lovén, 1836 * Evadne prolongata Behning 1938 * Evadne spinifera P. E. Müller, 1867 ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * Category:Cladocera
title: Evadne (crustacean)
